Requirements: Java, Python, ImageMagick, Unix-like system

Usage: 
Edit mosaic.sh: 
 
Run:
./mosaic.sh  

Swing window opens. Set layout in the string format: #pic_in_row1 #pic_in_row2 ... #pic_in_row[n] . 
Set final picture width and border (space between photos and around them). Selecting Auto Layout places 
photos in [sqrt(#photos)] rows, each having about the same number of pictures.

